    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">An unusual increase in the number of incidents caused by the exposure to bacteria either through skin contact, ingestion orinhalation. Examples include salmonella, MSRA, and cholera, among others.</skos:definition>
    <skos:notation>bacterialDisease</skos:notation>
